title: We're back baby!
itunes:title: We're back baby!
description:
The Breakfast Club is back, well not like they never left anyway, but they recorded for the first time live in the studio! They opened up the phone lines to see if any of our listeners had to deal with someone addicted to a drugs or anything else that was related Angela Yee's Lip Service episode. Moreover Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a Texas football team that called themselves the cotton pickers and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
